# Product Images Directory

This directory is for product images.

## How to Add Real Images:

1. Add your product images here with these names:
   - royal-canin-mini.jpg
   - royal-canin-mini-detail.jpg
   - hills-adult-cat.jpg
   - hills-adult-cat-detail.jpg
   - kong-classic-red.jpg
   - kong-classic-action.jpg
   - proplan-optiderma.jpg
   - acana-pacifica.jpg
   - catlit-clumping.jpg
   - temptations-chicken.jpg

2. Recommended image specifications:
   - Format: JPG or WebP
   - Size: 800x800px to 1200x1200px
   - Quality: 80-90%
   - File size: < 200KB each

3. Where to get images:
   - Product manufacturer websites
   - Official brand resources
   - Stock photo sites (with license)
   - Your own product photography

